column5: There's still some ice out there.. so watch where you are going...      And the water is a tad high at Lake St. John.    Second time in a year this guys had his floors washed unfortunately.
Wow that's nuts nice pictures from the sky though
A lot of them over there in that "boat" !
I aint afraid of that little bit of ice.  Maybe i will fish from it so i can use two rods.
Just nose up on it and drill two holes Glen !
